keel.Algorithms.Preprocess.Missing_Values.ConceptAllPossibleValues

Class valueAssociations

  • java.lang.Object
    • keel.Algorithms.Preprocess.Missing_Values.ConceptAllPossibleValues.valueAssociations

  • public class valueAssociations
extends java.lang.Object

    This class stores a frequency list of classes for a given value, i.e. for a same value in a attribute, it stores the number of times a determined class is associated with the value.

    Since:
    JDK 1.5

    Version:
    0.3
    Author:
    Written by Julián Luengo Martín 07/03/2006
